1
00:00:04,839 --> 00:00:07,489
C'mon, Fluttershy, it'll be fun!

2
00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:09,679
There's nothing fun about dragons!

3
00:00:09,830 --> 00:00:12,639
Scary, yes.
Fun, no!

4
00:00:12,790 --> 00:00:16,989
Fluttershy, the great dragon migration
happens only once in a generation.

5
00:00:17,140 --> 00:00:19,485
Do you really wanna pass up
a chance like that?

6
00:00:19,789 --> 00:00:21,489
Now that you put it that way,

7
00:00:21,719 --> 00:00:22,689
yes!

8
00:00:23,439 --> 00:00:26,099
Aw Fluttershy,
we just don't want you to miss out.

9
00:00:26,250 --> 00:00:28,139
Miss out on what? Dragons?

10
00:00:28,290 --> 00:00:31,589
Big, scaly, fire-breathing dragons?

11
00:00:31,740 --> 00:00:33,139
Well... yeah!

12
00:00:33,290 --> 00:00:35,259
Thanks, but... no thanks!

13
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:40,689
Look, Fluttershy, I watched that
boring butterfly migration with you,

14
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:43,839
so now it's your turn to watch
the dragon migration with me!

15
00:00:43,990 --> 00:00:44,899
You owe me!

16
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:47,301
I said... no!

17
00:00:57,219 --> 00:00:59,989
Okay, I guess
I'll let you off the hook this time.

18
00:01:02,302 --> 00:01:07,262
Season 2 | Episode 21
Dragon Quest

19
00:01:09,189 --> 00:01:12,939
Subbed and Timed by GrayJeager
GrayJeager@gmail.com

20
00:01:31,022 --> 00:01:35,326
http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3
